"      Cohen RD, Woseth DM, Thisted RA, Hanauer SB. A meta-analysis and overview of the literature on treatment options for left-sided ulcerative colitis and ulcerative proctitis. Am J Gastroenterol 2000; 95:1263.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"   </ol>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
