"     Deputy Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?10/39/10874/contributors\">",
"     Susan B Yeon, MD, JD, FACC",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
